<MainLayout title="Content SEO Services In The Philippines - Bright Forge SEO" description="Great content deserves to be seen. Our SEO content services in the Philippines help brands rank with strategy-first writing that drives results.">
  <LegacyHeader slot="header" />

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <Hero
    badgeIcon="fas fa-pen-nib"
    badgeText="Content SEO Experts"
    title="Content SEO Services In The Philippines"
    breadcrumbCurrent="Content SEO Services Philippines"
  >
    <Fragment slot="story">
      <p>Ever felt like you've done everything right—built a great website, designed eye-catching product pages, and shared posts on social media—yet still struggled to get noticed online? I've been there, too. A close friend once confided that her new e-commerce store had fantastic products but hardly any visitors. She thought she was missing some "secret sauce." Turns out, the key ingredient was well-structured, SEO-focused content.</p>

      <p>That's exactly what we offer here at Bright Forge SEO: carefully planned and brilliantly executed content that boosts visibility and sparks meaningful engagement. Our approach combines technical best practices with genuine storytelling, so you don't just rank—you connect with real people who are ready to become loyal customers.</p>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="actions">
      <ButtonPrimary href="/contact" text="Start Your Content Journey" />
      <ButtonSecondary href="#approach" text="See Our Process" />
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="visual">
      <div class="hero-image-container">
        <div class="content-icon-grid">
          <div class="content-icon"><i class="fas fa-pen-nib"></i></div>
          <div class="content-icon"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i></div>
          <div class="content-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div>
          <div class="content-icon"><i class="fas fa-users"></i></div>
          <div class="content-icon"><i class="fas fa-search"></i></div>
          <div class="content-icon"><i class="fas fa-heart"></i></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>

