    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Great Content Powers Your <span>SEO Success</span></h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content-explanation">
        <div class="content-card">
          <div class="content-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="content-text">
            <p>Content is more than just words. It's the vehicle that carries your brand's voice and connects you with real people online. Ranking well on Google is important, but your ultimate goal is to turn those clicks into leads, sales, and repeat customers.</p>
            
            <p>Our combination of data-driven keyword strategies, compelling narratives, and user-centric design strikes the perfect balance for search engines and readers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Section -->
