            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Strategic Keyword Research</h3>
              <p>We dig into the search terms your audience actually uses and position your content so it appears right where they're looking. This approach amplifies your visibility and puts you on track to land on those coveted SERPs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>SEO Copywriting</h3>
              <p>Our copywriting SEO services are designed to connect with people on a deeper level. By addressing real-life questions, frustrations, and interests, we help turn casual browsers into enthusiastic customers.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Content Optimization</h3>
              <p>Content that's optimized correctly tends to stay relevant over time. Through strategic planning, we make sure you get a steady flow of visitors who value what you offer—leading to long-term returns.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-item">
              <h3>Custom Content Strategy</h3>
              <p>Every business has its own story and audience. Whether you need direction for your content team or a complete overhaul, we'll shape a strategy that works for your unique journey.</p>
            </div>
