      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Our Content SEO <span>Process</span></h2>
        <p>Every business has its own story and audience. Wherever you are in your journey, we'll shape a strategy that works for you.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="process-grid">
        <div class="process-box orange-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-compass"></i>
          </div>
