            <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Keyword Research</h3>
          <p>We map out the specific search terms that can connect you to your audience and spot opportunities competitors may have missed.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-box white-bg">
          <div class="process-box-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-sliders-h"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Content Optimization</h3>
          <p>We revamp your title tags, headings, and overall structure. By making strategic tweaks, we help your pages shine in search rankings.</p>
        </div>

