            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>AI-Enhanced Writing</h3>
            <p>Human-refined content combining AI efficiency with editorial excellence and brand consistency.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Visual Content</h3>
            <p>High-quality graphics, videos, and interactive assets that boost engagement and conversions.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="benefit-card">
            <div class="benefit-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Proven Results</h3>
            <p>Data-driven approach with transparent reporting and continuous optimization for long-term success.</p>
